column2: SELECT TOP #  a.apogee_id,a.dec,cast(str(a.glat,#,#) as float) glat,cast(str(a.glon,#,#) as float) glon,cast(str(a.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,a.rv_feh,a.rv_logg,a.rv_teff,a.snr,a.starflag,a.verr,a.verr_med,a.vhelio_avg,a.vscatter,o.j,o.h,o.k  FROM apogeeStar as a  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.apstar_id = a.apstar_id  JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id=o.apogee_id  JOIN aspcapStar as q ON a.apstar_id=q.apstar_id
